ntCatData?.label || ''}`}\n            </div>\n            <HeroNextAchievement\n              achievement={nextAchievement}\n              accentOverride={heroAccent}\n              onTap={onAchievementTap}\n            />\n          </div>\n        );\n      })", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2413"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_awardstab", "callee": "map", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2509"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_awardstab", "callee": "map", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2608"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2622"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2623"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2624"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2625"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2626"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useState", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2627"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useToast", "source_file": "/Users/juandiego/Projects/Mentex app/screens/profile.jsx", "source_location": "L2629"}, {"caller_nid": "screens_profile_profilescreen", "callee": "useReducer", "source_fi